{"tid":756990,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"devast.io 呢類game真係好仆街","createTime":"2018-07-26T12:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T09:28:33.000Z","uid":30836,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07940f11f53d308aa7328de71b942984303ce16e","tid":756990,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"有好多成癮因素<br />\n儲素材、殺人、儲裝備、砌靚屋、好多嘢俾你去探索<br />\n<br />\n辛苦砌完間大屋<br />\n#1呢個仆街就會拎住支機關槍射鳩死你<br />\n乜都冇晒<br />\n<a href=\"http://starve.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarve.io&d=XOSbgD3UyiEruwmKbaO1DS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3393c2d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">starve.io</a>、<a href=\"http://nend.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnend.io&d=XOSbgD3UyiEruwmKbaO1DS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7d0fdd0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">nend.io</a>呢啲仆街game都千奇唔好玩<br />\n<br />\n又冇得pause 想屙尿都難<br />\n三五成群基本上可以稱霸個server<br />\n歧視毒撚 俾狗玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係minecraft好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9a5c6b4e1bb012c84d7118f98c17d9afb3ef52","tid":756990,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"肚餓個陣要點做<br />\n同埋邊度可以飲水?"},{"pid":"93a991021b3407034d829c92ec36fc9fe1cec21c","tid":756990,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9a5c6b4e1bb012c84d7118f98c17d9afb3ef52","tid":756990,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"肚餓個陣要點做<br />\n同埋邊度可以飲水?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://講緊starve.io?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AC%9B%E7%B7%8Astarve.io%3F&d=XOSbgD3UyiEruwmKbaO1DS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d9b2f061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">講緊starve.io?</a><br />\n建議你咪撚玩<br />\n呢隻game仲on9過新出嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n飲水要跳落河度飲<br />\n除非有bridge唔係一定會出現drown狀態<br />\n咁上下要上返水回氣<br />\n<br />\n最好喺湖邊起個火堆 一路保溫一路浸水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進階啲嘅玩法可以整bottle<br />\n咁裝完水就隨時隨地都可以飲<br />\n<br />\n但呢啲on9 game最好就咪撚玩<br />\n浪費人生<br />\n不如諗下堅持一日飲七至八杯水仲好"},{"pid":"9125dc54c5573e184227961a98132be5b614f1ac","tid":756990,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"我就黎玩下睇下會唔會用左我12粒鍾"},{"pid":"766ad8fb1693c9c9e86c71cc38d5991308dd07d1","tid":756990,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f9a5c6b4e1bb012c84d7118f98c17d9afb3ef52","tid":756990,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"肚餓個陣要點做<br />\n同埋邊度可以飲水?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"肚餓就搵梅食<br />\n最好一開波盡快整spear打狼打兔<br />\n然後喺火堆煮嚟食<br />\n<br />\n盡快入手craft book<br />\ncraft嘢可以快至少十倍<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好玩 浪費時間"},{"pid":"e87800225daa1ca50b66b1b68643a83f68ea3bc7","tid":756990,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"766ad8fb1693c9c9e86c71cc38d5991308dd07d1","tid":756990,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f9a5c6b4e1bb012c84d7118f98c17d9afb3ef52","tid":756990,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"肚餓個陣要點做<br />\n同埋邊度可以飲水?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"肚餓就搵梅食<br />\n最好一開波盡快整spear打狼打兔<br />\n然後喺火堆煮嚟食<br />\n<br />\n盡快入手craft book<br />\ncraft嘢可以快至少十倍<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好玩 浪費時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"屌 原來係溫度計黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a87478dadcbd9e44f88268c267a4dadc877713","tid":756990,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9125dc54c5573e184227961a98132be5b614f1ac","tid":756990,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"我就黎玩下睇下會唔會用左我12粒鍾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"唔會 基本上如果你唔係由開ser開始玩<br />\n實有啲dominator